articles.title: The P7 peptide antagonizes bFGF-induced malignant behaviors of ovarian cancer by inhibiting MEK/ERK signaling pathway.
articles.summary: P7 peptide effectively blocks ovarian cancer cell growth and spread by disrupting a key molecular pathway triggered by basic fibroblast growth factor.
